# CFCharacterSetGetPredefined(_:)

**Function**

Returns a predefined character set.

## Declaration

```swift
func CFCharacterSetGetPredefined(_ theSetIdentifier: CFCharacterSetPredefinedSet) -> CFCharacterSet!
```

## Parameters

- **theSetIdentifier**: A predefined character set. See [doc://com.apple.corefoundation/documentation/CoreFoundation/predefined_cfcharacterset_selector_values] for the list of available character sets.

## Return Value

A predefined character set. This instance is owned by Core Foundation.
